data.description: Less than 20 min to New Smyrna Beach! This home built in 2022 with upgrades awaits! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 Living areas plus a dining room. The open Kitchen is spacious and includes a pantry for plenty of storage space. This home has many recent upgrades: Vinyl Fencing, Hurricane Shutters, 10x12 Shed with ramp, Reclaimed water system, custom blinds throughout, gutters, PLUS extended patio for entertaining or relaxing in the privacy of your backyard AND close to Shopping!
